General.Name: Priortech
General.Description: Priortech Ltd, through its subsidiaries, develops, manufactures, and markets optical systems for automatic testing and measurement in Israel and internationally. It offers machines, semiconductors, semiconductor components, semiconductor wafers, and electronic substrates. Priortech Ltd was incorporated in 1980 and is based in Migdal HaEmek, Israel.
